title: Inspire San Diego Launch Party
text: Inspire San Diego Launch Party OCT 05, 6:54 pm Inspire San Diego, which benefits inner-city and homeless youth in San Diego, is throwing a launch party on Monday, October 19, inviting all singles to Fluxx in downtown where all proceeds from ticket sales and the charity auction will go to Inspire San Diego.
